title: Playdigo
text: A full-stack web application for managing Playdigo's advertising operations. It combines a modern dashboard UI with a secure backend server, handling everything from data visualization and user interaction to authentication, databases, and cloud infrastructure.

title: Insight Genie
text: Developed the full website and backend for InsightGenie, including secure APIs that connect banks to AI models providing credit and risk insights in markets lacking such systems. Built scalable infrastructure, managed client API integrations, and delivered dashboards and analytics tools enabling companies to assess applicants and banks to offer informed lending.
